msgstr "ຍົກເລີກການນຳໃຊ້ຄີການມອບໝາຍຜູ້ໃຊ້ Azure ທີ່ຢູ່ໃນແຄສ"

#. module: cloud_storage_azure
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/cloud_storage_azure/models/res_config_settings.py:0
msgid ""
"Some Azure attachments are in use, please migrate their cloud storages "
"before disable this module"
msgstr ""
"ມີສິ່ງຄັດຕິດ Azure ບາງຢ່າງກຳລັງຖືກນຳໃຊ້ຢູ່, ກະລຸນາຍ້າຍຂໍ້ມູນການເກັບຮັກສາຄລາວຂອງພວກມັນ ກ່ອນທີ່ຈະປິດກາ"
"ນນຳໃຊ້ມໍດູນນີ້"

#. module: cloud_storage_azure
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/cloud_storage_azure/models/res_config_settings.py:0
msgid ""
"The connection string is not allowed to download blobs from the container.\n"
"%s"
msgstr ""
"ຊຸດຂໍ້ຄວາມການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ ບໍ່ໄດ້ຮັບອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ດາວໂຫລດ blobs ຈາກຄອນເທນເນີ.\n"
"%s"

#. module: cloud_storage_azure
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/cloud_storage_azure/models/res_config_settings.py:0
msgid ""
"The connection string is not allowed to upload blobs to the container.\n"
"%s"
msgstr ""
"ຊຸດຂໍ້ຄວາມການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ ບໍ່ໄດ້ຮັບອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ອັບໂຫລດ blobs ໄປຫາຄອນເທນເນີ.\n"
"%s"
